<C>__{klute}
<D>__{mm.}
<A>__{she smiles again, hands the letter and wallet back out, closes the door (doesn't slam, just closes). klute looks at it blankly for a time, starts to knock again, decides not to turns and descends the stairs.}
<B>__{bree}
<A>__{bree listens through the door to his departing foot steps. they fade from hearing. she hastens to assemble her properties.}
